      Humanity found a way into  the depths  of the  space.  First  brave
      hearts set off to grasp the unknown. It found them first. Dreams of
      pathfinders crashed against the cold flesh of the space. Now and on
      only  one  thing  matters:  what are  you capable  of  to  survive?
      Dispatcher is a first-person horror  with RPG  elements.  The  game
      takes place in the near future on a spaceship Dispatcher which crew
      got into an accident and trapped with alien monsters.
